Investigator, Being very experienced with ghost hunting, he is the one that figures out the ghost type by using evidences and abilities.
Journalist, The journalist documents everything he comes accross during the investigation. He takes photographs, videos and audio recordings and notes them down on the board. He also has an enormous bone collection.
Tracker, The tracker is fully equipped with sensors. He uses those along with the old fashioned "salt trick" to track the ghost's every movemet and sound.
Psychic, Their special powers have allowed them to communicate with the other side. He can influence the ghost with cursed possessions and can talk to the ghost with a spirit box.
Guardian, They're nimble and quick to react and protect their team by taking precautions such as crucifixes and using incense to stun ghosts.
Electrician, Having years of electrical engineering experience, he can quickly fix any broken breaker.
Pharmacist, Having worked at a pharmaceutical company for decades before being fired for believing in the supernatural, they can prescribe sanity increasing medicine to those who have lost it during investigations.